Class MiddleEarthNode

  • Object
    • MiddleEarthNode
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Being, Place, Root

    public abstract class MiddleEarthNode
extends Object
    This abstract class represents people and places you may encounter as you search for The One Ring. (it is a name substitue for MountainCave, with some slight design improvements, no functional changes in relation to the driver/hunter classes).
    Author:
    AndrewStefanich
    See Also:
    Being, Place, Root
